headline: Zacks Industry Outlook Highlights ConocoPhillips, Occidental and National Fuel Gas
summary: Despite lower oil prices and rising renewable demand, ConocoPhillips, Occidental, and National Fuel Gas are positioned to weather headwinds in the U.S. integrated energy space.
